indent(2,space)
Case: T7 Strategy Insertion - Minimal Regression
/*
  Minimal test for T7 (Strategy Insertion).
  Expectation:
    - G10 has supporters and no Strategy child -> becomes a candidate and is rewritten:
      insert Strategy S10a insertedStrategy: and rehang its former children under it.
    - G20 already has a Strategy child -> not a candidate.
*/

Goal G0 top:
  System property holds.

  Goal G10 needsStrategy:
    Some claim requiring an explicit strategy place.

    Strategy S10a insertedStrategy:
      AUTHOR CHECK: The evidence will show that the subclaims below are sufficient to support this goal.

      Goal G10a strategySupport:
        AUTHOR CHECK: The evidence supports the claim stated above.

        Evidence E101 someEvidence:
          Tool: Example Tool.
          The evidence records a property.

  Goal G20 alreadyHasStrategy:
    Another claim.

    Strategy S20 existingStrategy:
      AUTHOR CHECK: Existing strategy.

      Evidence E201 otherEvidence:
        Tool: Example Tool.
        The evidence records another property.

